{% comment %}
  custom-header-pill.liquid
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Custom header styling for Florida Tea and Honey (KICK-inspired look).

  What it does (desktop only, >= 750px):
    - Wraps the centered nav menu + search in a rounded "pill" capsule.
    - Adds a thin vertical divider between the menu and the search icon.
    - Turns the right-hand action icons (account, cart) into circular buttons.

  Design notes:
    - Colors are NOT hard-coded. All fills/borders derive from the theme's
      own --color-foreground-rgb at low opacity, so they adapt to whatever
      color scheme is configured in the theme editor.
    - The search icon lands in the center column because search_position is set
      to "center" in sections/header-group.json (the header-row snippet honors
      a "center" value even though the admin dropdown only lists left/right).

  To revert: delete this file and remove its {% render %} call in
  sections/header.liquid, then set search_position back to "right".
{% endcomment %}
<style>
  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    /* --- Center nav pill: wraps menu + search --- */
    .header__column--center {
      --pill-border: rgb(var(--color-foreground-rgb) / 0.28);
      --pill-bg: rgb(var(--color-foreground-rgb) / 0.12);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--gap-lg, 1.25rem);
      padding-block: 0.55rem;
      padding-inline: 1.75rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--pill-border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--pill-bg);
    }

    /* Thin vertical divider before the search icon, inside the pill */
    .header__column--center .search-action {
      margin-inline-start: 0.25rem;
      padding-inline-start: 1.25rem;
      border-inline-start: 1px solid var(--pill-border);
    }

    /* --- Right-side circular icon buttons (account + cart) --- */
    .header__column--right .header-actions__action:not(.localization-selector) {
      inline-size: 2.75rem;
      block-size: 2.75rem;
      border: 1px solid rgb(var(--color-foreground-rgb) / 0.18);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-grid;
      place-items: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }

    .header__column--right .header-actions__action:not(.localization-selector):hover {
      background: rgb(var(--color-foreground-rgb) / 0.08);
      border-color: rgb(var(--color-foreground-rgb) / 0.3);
    }
  }

  /* On mobile the menu collapses to a drawer; keep the native layout and let
     the theme's drawer search handle search instead of the centered icon. */
  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .header__column--center .search-action {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
